This paper discusses the implementation and auditing of differentially private systems, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also mentions the use of differential privacy in data management (cs.DB), machine learning (cs.LG), and social networks (cs.SI). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of unit testing for differential privacy, which could fall under the category of cybernetics (cs.CY).
